    This application was developed in Swift for iOS 10, using the XCode IDE. It
    is suited for any iOS Device, iPad 5 up through iPad Pro 12.9". It represents
    the classic 2-player game where players alternate taking turns launching missiles at
    the other player's board until all 5 ships on one player's board have been sunk.
    Some key elements of the application are:
    <div style="float: left; margin-top: 10px; margin-left: 10px">
      <ul>
        <li>Saves the application state even if the app is closed down and restarted.</li>
        <li>When a player takes a shot, they alerted as to whether the result was a hit/miss/sunk ship.</li>
        <li>Application randomly generates a valid board upon game creation.</li>
        <li>Once the game has been completed, both player's boards are completely visible, however all <br> buttons become disabled.</li>
        <li>Rotation has been disabled due to the fact that when the screen is in landscape orientation, <br> there isn't enough room to properly display the boards.</li>
        <li>Ability to add/delete games.</li>
        <li>A list of all active games is displayed from the main screen.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
